58
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:42,530
he'll take it through war.

59
00:03:42,970 --> 00:03:43,970
Exactly.

60
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,360
So,

61
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:48,060
handing it over

62
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,300
doesn't really matter.

63
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:51,690
The dignified Lord of Wei

64
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:54,530
wouldn't go back on his word, right?

65
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,690
The feud between us

66
