233
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,320
- to drinking well water.
- How kind.

234
00:11:44,330 --> 00:11:46,480
But the wells in the city
have been dry for days.

235
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:47,980
It's all right. Don't worry.

236
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:49,020
We'll fix it together.

237
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:50,410
- Shall we?
- Yes.

238
00:11:50,410 --> 00:11:52,150
