269
00:13:40,810 --> 00:13:42,140
because they long for you too?

270
00:13:43,810 --> 00:13:45,260
I didn't mean that.

271
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:48,330
The people treat me kindly

272
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:50,650
because they long for you,

273
00:13:51,900 --> 00:13:53,530
waiting to see what you want.

274
00:13:55,450 --> 00:13:56,860
Everyone knows

275
00:13:57,330 --> 00:13:58,930
