You're good with words,

284
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:22,980
twisting things around

285
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:24,240
just to get me to marry you.

286
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:27,650
This is the will of the people.

287
00:14:29,170 --> 00:14:31,260
So why not go with the people's will

288
00:14:31,650 --> 00:14:33,450
and hand over the seal of Panyi to me

289
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:35,410
so we can get married soon?

290
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:45,220
Xindu has always been part of Wei.

291
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:47,500
I share the people's will and purpose.

292
00:14:48,380 --> 00:14:50,530
Li Su was the first to sow discord,

293
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:52,930
and now you play mind games.

294
00:14:54,410 --> 00:14:55,690
You both disgust me.

295
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,740
Don't think for a second

296
00:15:01,740 --> 00:15:03,450
that I'm as easy to fool
as my grandfather.

297
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:11,780
As for the seal,

298
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:14,730
I suggest you make your decision soon.

299
00:15:16,050 --> 00:15:17,290
I have some patience

300
00:15:18,020 --> 00:15:18,860
but

301
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:20,410
not much.

302
00:15:29,650 --> 00:15:30,740
The Lord of Wei

303
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:33,170
really is cold as stone.

304
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:37,410
If he were so easily persuaded,

305
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:39,140
it wouldn't be trustworthy.

306
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:40,100
So,

307
00:15:40,570 --> 00:15:41,810
what do we do now?

308
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,500
My heart is like water,

309
00:15:47,170 --> 00:15:48,690
and water wears down stone.

310
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:54,330
Turns out Lady Qiao is pretty tough.

311
00:15:55,290 --> 00:15:56,500
The Lord fought day and night

312
00:15:56,500 --> 00:15:57,740
just to reclaim Xindu.

313
00:15:58,020 --> 00:16:00,140
Those flowers should be offered to him.

314
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,980
The Lord doesn't care for flowers.

315
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:05,140
Otherwise, he'd be like a weak woman.

316
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:06,340
Right.

317
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,690
Lady Qiao has managed to do

318
00:16:07,690 --> 00:16:08,720
what the Lord has failed.

319
00:16:08,860 --> 00:16:10,030
That's what's bothering him.

320
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,570
Good for you.

321
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:14,100
You're usually like a mute,

322
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,730
but now you've hit the nail on the head.

323
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:17,380
Hey, give it to me.

324
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,890
- Whoa.
- Catch it.

325
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,140
My Lord, please spare us.

326
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:33,260
We didn't see you there

327
00:16:33,290 --> 00:16:34,220
and offended you.

328
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:36,330
Are those flowers meant for Lady Qiao?

329
00:16:39,050 --> 00:16:40,260
They are for you, My Lord.

330
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:41,410
You're a renowned

331
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:42,380
brave fighter.

332
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,230
I...

333
00:16:43,330 --> 00:16:44,220
I heard

334
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:46,900
you'll be the new lord of Xindu,

335
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:49,170
and Lady Qiao is to be your wife.

336
00:16:49,170 --> 00:16:50,620
So, I passed them to her.

337
00:16:51,330 --> 00:16:52,780
Fine, hand them here.

338
00:16:52,780 --> 00:16:54,050
I'll hold them for the Lord.

339
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:54,900
From now on,

340
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,690
don't bring useless things like this.

341
00:16:56,930 --> 00:16:57,980
- Go now.
- Yes.

342
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:59,700
Thank you, My Lord.

343
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:02,690
Who says the Lord doesn't have
the people's support?

344
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:05,220
Seems to me the commoners know
who their lord is.

345
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:07,130
Then why won't they come and register

346
00:17:07,130 --> 00:17:08,150
to collect their food?

347
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:10,980
Give them more time.

348
00:17:11,260 --> 00:17:13,090
The thick ice didn't freeze in a day.

349
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:15,370
I've got some patience left.

350
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:16,780
Let's go.

351
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:17,820
Hyah.

352
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:19,660
Hyah.

353
00:17:19,780 --> 00:17:20,740
Mayor.

354
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:21,740
Help us.

355
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:23,950
Wei Shao's killing people
in the streets on horseback.

356
00:17:23,950 --> 00:17:25,700
They've been counting households
every day

357
00:17:25,700 --> 00:17:27,570
just so they can kill
all of us border folk.

358
00:17:27,570 --> 00:17:30,050
They're trying to steal our food.

359
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,770
Even good families can't protect

360
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,520
(Zhen Mansion)
their daughters anymore.

361
00:17:33,530 --> 00:17:36,220
Yeah, they treat lives like weeds.

362
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:38,610
Xindu has changed hands.

363
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,740
I'm no longer your mayor.

364
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,850
Though you have reclaimed lost land,

365
00:17:53,130 --> 00:17:55,020
the people of Xindu today

366
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:57,700
are no longer subjects of Wei.

367
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:01,050
You wish to win them over quickly,

368
00:18:01,570 --> 00:18:03,700
but they've been poisoned
by Li Su's lies.

369
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:06,460
They may not understand
your intentions at once.

370
00:18:07,370 --> 00:18:08,500
Besides,

371
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:11,020
you didn't take Xindu

372
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:13,420
just to get revenge.

373
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:16,850
You have greater ambitions

374
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:20,810
and will need the people's help.

375
00:18:25,220 --> 00:18:26,060
My Lord,

376
00:18:27,050 --> 00:18:29,530
governing people is like managing water.

377
00:18:31,090 --> 00:18:32,050
You can't rush it.

378
00:18:34,890 --> 00:18:36,850
Now, let's see who runs out

379
00:18:38,370 --> 00:18:39,810
of patience first between me and her.

380
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:46,320
(People's Wall, Wei State)

381
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:48,020
Back in the battle of Xindu,

382
00:18:48,130 --> 00:18:51,260
countless families
lost their sons and husbands.

383
00:18:51,890 --> 00:18:53,850
After Li Su entered the city,

384
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:56,180
he forbade the people
from collecting the bodies

385
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:57,420
and burying their loved ones.

386
00:18:58,020 --> 00:19:00,090
So, whenever the people
could leave the city,

387
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:02,330
they would sneak out
to the eastern battlefield

388
00:19:02,330 --> 00:19:04,090
to find their relatives' belongings,

389
00:19:04,390 --> 00:19:06,620
hide them in their clothes,
and smuggle them back in.

390
00:19:07,810 --> 00:19:08,850
This wall

391
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:12,290
was built from those very keepsakes.

392
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:14,020
But

393
00:19:14,610 --> 00:19:15,780
as the years passed,

394
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:18,850
people gradually turned this place

395
00:19:18,850 --> 00:19:21,090
into a shrine for prayers,

396
00:19:21,530 --> 00:19:22,660
forgetting

397
00:19:23,050 --> 00:19:24,940
(Nanny Zhong, Lady Xu's maid)
its true meaning.

398
00:19:25,370 --> 00:19:27,610
To the people, this wall is a place

399
00:19:27,850 --> 00:19:29,980
to grieve their loved ones.

400
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:32,770
To the Lord,

401
00:19:34,260 --> 00:19:36,260
it's a memorial to the dead.

402
00:19:36,690 --> 00:19:38,440
I came to Xindu this time

403
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,980
to ensure the marriage

404
00:19:39,980 --> 00:19:42,060
between you and the Lord,

405
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:44,660
so Lady Xu can be at peace.

406
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:46,420
This is a wishing plate.

407
00:19:47,050 --> 00:19:48,050
May your marriage

408
00:19:48,050 --> 00:19:49,330
go smoothly.

409
00:19:51,570 --> 00:19:52,410
Thank you.

410
00:19:52,410 --> 00:19:54,220
(Stay united as one;
do not part in anger)

411
00:20:03,980 --> 00:20:05,420
(Stay in health; grow old together)

412
00:20:10,810 --> 00:20:11,460
Where's Wei Duo?

413
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:12,980
Didn't I order all this cleared away?

414
00:20:12,980 --> 00:20:13,800
Why is it still here?

415
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:14,600
My Lord,

416
00:20:14,610 --> 00:20:16,680
the people have kept this habit
for over a decade.

417
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:19,330
It's understandable
they can't change overnight.

418
00:20:42,130 --> 00:20:43,150
What are you doing here?

419
00:20:51,370 --> 00:20:52,210
My Lord.

420
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:55,130
I'm praying for the people.

421
00:20:55,130 --> 00:20:56,090
Praying?

422
00:20:59,370 --> 00:21:00,850
Do you know what this place is

423
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:07,610
and why this wall

424
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:10,090
was built?

425
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:18,370
How can you let her pray here?

426
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:25,850
How many of you still remember

427
00:21:26,890 --> 00:21:28,460
why this wall exists

428
00:21:30,890 --> 00:21:32,360
and who should be responsible for it?

429
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:34,860
Come on.

430
00:21:36,090 --> 00:21:37,500
Take all this down and burn it.

431
00:21:38,130 --> 00:21:39,090
Burn it all.

432
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:41,220
- My Lord, please don't.
- You can't burn it.

433
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:43,500
My Lord, you can't burn it.

434
00:21:54,020 --> 00:21:55,330
You're ruthless.

435
00:21:55,330 --> 00:21:57,130
You're not fit to rule Xindu.

436
00:21:57,290 --> 00:21:58,330
You don't deserve it.

437
00:22:06,780 --> 00:22:07,620
My Lord,

438
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:09,780
Zhen Zhi used to work for the late lord.

439
00:22:10,020 --> 00:22:11,420
When Xindu fell,

440
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:13,050
he surrendered to Li Su

441
00:22:13,050 --> 00:22:14,290
to protect the people.

442
00:22:14,660 --> 00:22:16,130
My Lord, please calm your anger.

443
00:22:17,020 --> 00:22:18,850
My Lord, please spare the mayor.

444
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:22,090
Please spare the mayor.

445
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:25,700
My Lord, please spare the mayor.

446
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:29,370
He's a good man.

447
00:22:33,780 --> 00:22:37,220
The Lord watched with his own eyes
as his father, brothers, and people

448
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,850
were slaughtered.

449
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:41,740
How can he let that go so easily?

450
00:22:42,740 --> 00:22:46,220
That's exactly why Lady Xu
wants to forge

451
00:22:46,290 --> 00:22:47,740
a marriage alliance with Yanzhou.

452
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:50,570
Lady Xu feels sorry

453
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:53,090
for the Lord.

454
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:55,980
She hopes he can move on

455
00:22:56,420 --> 00:22:58,180
and live with less pain.

456
00:22:58,610 --> 00:23:00,570
My Lady, what are you thinking?

457
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:04,610
I think I know what he needs.

458
00:23:07,740 --> 00:23:09,420
Li Su was a thief,

459
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,220
and you, Wei Shao,

460
00:23:11,940 --> 00:23:13,460
are no better.

461
00:23:14,290 --> 00:23:17,260
Back then, Li Su's army
pillaged the city for grain.

462
00:23:17,420 --> 00:23:18,940
Now, you take control of Xindu

463
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:20,050
and force the people

464
00:23:20,050 --> 00:23:22,570
to offer food, wine, and women.

465
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:26,220
How are you any different from Li Su?

466
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:28,220
Yes, you're just like him.

467
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,420
Exactly the same.

468
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:31,220
The late lord was a righteous man.

469
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:32,890
You are

470
00:23:34,370 --> 00:23:36,610
unworthy to be his heir.

471
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:39,180
My life is nothing,

472
00:23:40,660 --> 00:23:41,500
but I pity...

473
00:23:42,260 --> 00:23:43,500
What a pity that Xindu

474
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:46,530
has fallen into a bandit's hands.

475
00:23:47,220 --> 00:23:48,070
My Lord,

476
00:23:48,090 --> 00:23:49,290
kill this man now.

477
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:50,980
We can't let him confuse the public.

478
00:23:51,020 --> 00:23:51,890
Yes, My Lord.

479
00:23:52,090 --> 00:23:53,000
Yes. Let's kill him.

480
00:23:53,010 --> 00:23:54,560
- Kill him.
- We can't let him live.

481
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:55,420
My Lord,

482
00:23:55,850 --> 00:23:57,260
if you kill Zhen Zhi,

483
00:23:57,290 --> 00:23:59,020
everything we've worked for
will be ruined.

484
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:01,130
Please punish him severely.

485
00:24:01,330 --> 00:24:02,980
We fought so hard for Xindu.

486
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:04,220
Was it for these people

487
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,990
to insult even our ancestors?

488
00:24:08,220 --> 00:24:09,570
My Lady, must you go?

489
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:11,420
This could put you in danger.

490
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:12,880
My Lord,

491
00:24:12,890 --> 00:24:14,220
you must execute him.

492
00:24:15,730 --> 00:24:18,180
- Kill him, My Lord.
- Just say the word.

493
00:24:19,180 --> 00:24:21,330
I have something to say to the Lord.

494
00:24:24,700 --> 00:24:25,610
Just in time.

495
00:24:28,290 --> 00:24:29,290
Let her in.

496
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:38,180
This started because of you.

497
00:24:38,780 --> 00:24:40,110
Aren't you going to say anything?

498
00:24:40,610 --> 00:24:42,460
I just did a divination.

499
00:24:42,610 --> 00:24:44,850
The wedding date is in three days.

500
00:24:44,940 --> 00:24:47,130
If we miss it,
we'll have to wait a long time.

501
00:24:48,330 --> 00:24:50,290
You keep delaying the marriage

502
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:52,570
because you just took control of Xindu

503
00:24:52,570 --> 00:24:54,130
and have been busy rebuilding it.

504
00:24:55,050 --> 00:24:56,810
But now, the people

505
00:24:56,890 --> 00:24:58,420
don't obey you

506
00:24:58,590 --> 00:24:59,940
or listen to your orders.

507
00:25:00,260 --> 00:25:03,290
Will you have your soldiers

508
00:25:03,370 --> 00:25:05,660
spend their days
making bricks and mortar?

509
00:25:08,220 --> 00:25:09,460
I have a plan

510
00:25:09,660 --> 00:25:11,260
to ease your troubles.

511
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,570
Most of Xindu's people

512
00:25:14,670 --> 00:25:17,700
are migrants from the borderlands.

513
00:25:18,020 --> 00:25:20,420
Since they refuse to submit,

514
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:22,090
why not

515
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:25,180
make an example of them?

516
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:27,500
Kill one to warn the rest.

517
00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:29,940
If one's not enough, kill ten.

518
00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:31,790
If ten's not enough, kill a hundred.

519
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:32,940
Keep killing until they obey.

520
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:33,780
You...

521
00:25:33,780 --> 00:25:35,330
You venomous woman.

522
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,750
With this,

523
00:25:36,940 --> 00:25:39,130
we can marry sooner.

524
00:25:39,130 --> 00:25:41,330
As expected
of that jerk's granddaughter.

525
00:25:41,330 --> 00:25:42,890
You wicked thing.

526
00:25:46,190 --> 00:25:48,480
Last night he tried to kill the Lord,

527
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:50,460
and now he dares insult me.

528
00:25:50,610 --> 00:25:51,810
We can't let him live.

529
00:25:52,340 --> 00:25:53,810
We don't have to slaughter the city,

530
00:25:53,810 --> 00:25:55,670
but at least his entire clan
should be executed

531
00:25:55,670 --> 00:25:56,800
to eliminate future threats.

532
00:25:56,810 --> 00:25:57,890
How vicious.

533
00:26:16,250 --> 00:26:17,140
My Lady...

534
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:18,100
My Lord.

535
00:26:20,610 --> 00:26:22,180
If I follow your advice,

536
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:24,660
how would I be any different from Li Su?

537
00:26:25,980 --> 00:26:27,880
Your grandfather's betrayal
brought me to ruin.

538
00:26:28,370 --> 00:26:29,890
And now you try to sway me

539
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:31,700
into slaughtering a city

540
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:33,050
for your sake?

541
00:26:34,130 --> 00:26:35,810
You viper.

542
00:26:35,980 --> 00:26:37,530
That's right. She's a viper.

543
00:26:37,530 --> 00:26:39,940
- Kill her.
- That viper. Kill her.

544
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:40,780
My Lord,

545
00:26:42,780 --> 00:26:43,700
please calm yourself.

546
00:26:43,700 --> 00:26:46,290
Kill her.

547
00:26:46,890 --> 00:26:48,020
Please calm yourself.

548
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:53,980
I was ignorant.

549
00:26:55,260 --> 00:26:56,660
Please forgive me.

550
00:26:58,020 --> 00:26:59,370
I will never forgive you.

551
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:07,180
You're so cruel.

552
00:27:07,530 --> 00:27:09,050
You will not meet a good end.

553
00:27:09,370 --> 00:27:11,090
You won't meet a good end.

554
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:14,290
This started because of Lady Qiao.

555
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:16,810
I will never fall for her schemes

556
00:27:17,570 --> 00:27:19,370
to turn me against the people of Xindu.

557
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,850
As for the mayor...

558
00:27:42,850 --> 00:27:44,290
You only pleaded for the people.

559
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:45,890
You're blameless.

560
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,610
Please rise.

561
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,020
My Lord,

562
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:12,850
you're just like the late lord.

563
00:28:14,810 --> 00:28:16,810
After 14 years of Xindu

564
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,290
under the enemy's rule,

565
00:28:20,780 --> 00:28:22,570
at last, we are back.

